#include <iostream>
#include <cmath>

using namespace std;
typedef long long int64;

bool is_square(int64 n){
	int64 s = sqrt(n);
	return (n == (s*s));
}

int main(){
	int64 T, N;
	cin >> T;
	while(T--){
		cin >> N;
		if(is_square(5*N*N+4) || is_square(5*N*N-4))
			cout << "is fibo" << endl;
		else
			cout << "not fibo" << endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
